ygData.messageBody:
Greetings Dark friends,

I just made level 16 today and I am very excited about testing it out. I
wanted some suggestions on where to hunt between level 16 and 20. I have
heard from you all saying that the Karanas and Lake Rathe are good. Please,
any advise would be appreciated.

Oh, and the stormy weather? Well I live in Myrtle Beach and Hurricane Floyd
is dropping in to say hello=(

Lalandra
16th level (finally)
Human Witch
Tunare
